('TXT_KEY_LEADER_NTF_CORNPLANTER_DONT_SETTLE_NO_1',                              'We have been planting and living off these lands through hundreds of summers and winters. Do not think that your recent arrival is a reason for us to stop.'),
('TXT_KEY_LEADER_NTF_CORNPLANTER_DONT_SETTLE_YES_1',                             'We respect your claim on these lands, and only ask that in return, you treat us with similar respect.'),
('TXT_KEY_LEADER_NTF_CORNPLANTER_LUXURY_TRADE_1',                                'Yes, we accept. This is the way to friendship between our nations.'),
('TXT_KEY_LEADER_NTF_CORNPLANTER_OPEN_BORDERS_EXCHANGE_1',                       'Let us travel freely in your lands. We will allow you to do the same.'),
('TXT_KEY_LEADER_NTF_CORNPLANTER_RESPONSE_REQUEST_1',                            'Come, in the times that are arriving, we will need your help in this matter.'),
