('TXT_KEY_LEADER_NTF_CORNPLANTER_DOW_GENERIC_1',                                 'You will see the might of the Seneca on the battlefield. It will be the sight that haunts your eyes as your head hangs on a spear.'),
('TXT_KEY_LEADER_NTF_CORNPLANTER_DOW_GENERIC_2',                                 'Or warriors will strike deep into your heart and drive you and your ways away from our Nation.'),
